<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/37905091/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u37905091-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/37905091/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">旧夏社</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-09-27"
      class="main-meta">2011-09-27 20:21:22</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5110272_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我初中高中历史课，每次考试都会考到这个天朝田亩制啊。夸它是革命纲领，思想结晶。意义一大堆。 老唐一笔带过，说这宗社会主义的土改方案，和孙中山的《建国方略》一样，一天也没有实施过。 其实我想听他多818的。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5110272/#comments">(1回应)</a>
